    "       - Poison control: 0 800 59 59 59 (France, antipoison numbers vary by region)",
    "       - Drug info: Drogues Info Service 0 800 23 13 13",
    "       - Quebec: 1 866 APPELLE (suicide), SOS Violence Conjugale 1 800 363 9010",
    "       - Belgium: 1813 (suicide BE-FR), Écoute Violences Conjugales 0800 30 030",
